0.15.1 Release "Endless Excursion"
----------------------------------

This is a special bug fix release to prevent PiTiVi from entering an endless
recursion, due to a change introduced in the GStreamer "good" plugins.
This ensures PiTiVi keeps working with the latest gst releases.

Translations have also been updated.

Dependencies/requirements have been unchanged since the 0.15 release.

== Hard requirements ==
  * gstreamer >= 0.10.28
  * gst-python >= 0.10.19
  * gnonlin >= 0.10.16
  * pygtk >= 2.18.0
  * pygtk >= 2.24.0
  * Python >= 2.5
  * zope.interface (http://www.zope.org/Products/ZopeInterface)
  * setuptools (http://peak.telecommunity.com/DevCenter/setuptools)
  * pygoocanvas (http://live.gnome.org/GooCanvas)
  * pyxdg (http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/pyxdg)

== Soft requirements ==
  * frei0r for the transformation feature
  * Numpy for the auto aligner feature

The PiTiVi team recommends satisfying those dependencies as much as possible
for an optimal user experience.

